headline: Comcast (CMCSA) Completes High-Speed Internet Expansion in Georgia with $10,000 Community Grant
summary: Comcast (CMCSA) recently concluded a successful broadband expansion in McDuffie County, Georgia, enhancing digital access for local communities and businesses. Despite these positive developments, Comcast’s share price fell by 2.61% during the past week. This decline occurred alongside broader market gains, as the Nasdaq reached record highs due to a tech stock rally led by Apple.
